            <div class="group">
                <h2><a href="/bong-ban" data-role="none">B&#243;ng B&#224;n</a></h2>
                <div class="list">
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="image">
                                    <div class="bg" style="background-image:url(https://cdn.sachtaman.com/data/Template/136cd41c-f0db-4f69-b82a-e44aa18bf95c/images/bg.jpg);"></div>
